    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290560</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_100_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダメ、なの……！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It...didn't...work!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_100_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊晶核の身の我らは
あまりにも脆弱すぎる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We could manifest the Atomism Cores properly.
However, our powers proved too weak!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290784</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_100_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊晶核を操るに足る
それなりの魔法の素地を
持った術者が必要じゃ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Our Atomism Core manipulation was insufficient.
We need the Lord of the Four Elements!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_100_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>術者を探すのら～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's impossible without hiiiim!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290924</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_100_030_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>術者ったって……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Lord of the what...!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_100_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うわっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Woaah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_100_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここは危ないよ！
とにかく逃げよう……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's too dangerous around here! Let's get away!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
